description: Susan G. Komen for the Cure Southwest Florida provides breast health education and grants funding to local agencies to assist breast cancer patients in navigating through the continuum of care. 75% of the money raised stays in our community and is granted out to local agencies to assist those in need. The other 25% goes directly to research to honor our promise to save lives and end breast cancer forever.\n\n###COL###
name: SUSAN G. KOMEN FOR THE CURE - SOUTHWEST FLORIDA
